{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game Concept</strong></h2>In Bubumbu you will help little puzzle pieces explore various worlds in search of the place they belong. The object portrayed on the puzzle pieces gives a hint to where they may fit. The interaction and logic reminds a lot of point-and-click adventures, and the challenge is similar that of a hidden objects game. <br> <br> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303420/extras/Bubumbu_11.gif?t=1733339670\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Secrets All Around</strong></h2>In addition to the main puzzle mechanics, the game worlds also contain hidden things around the environment. By pressing certain details you spot in your surroundings you may discover these secrets and get rewarded with achievements!<br> <br> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303420/extras/Bubumbu_12.gif?t=1733339670\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303420/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733339670","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303420/page.bg.jpg?t=1733339670","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303420/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733339670","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303420/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733339670","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3209120,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game Concept</strong></h2>In Bubumbu you will help little puzzle pieces explore various worlds in search of the place they belong. The object portrayed on the puzzle pieces gives a hint to where they may fit. The interaction and logic reminds a lot of point-and-click adventures, and the challenge is simil